\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f5\fs24\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f0 There are five 
psionic attack modes and five psionic defense modes. Each mode is like a specialized psionic power and generally follows the rules for using a psionic power, but there are some differences. Successful psionic attacks deal temporary ability damage, while s
uccessful psionic defenses protect the subject from taking that ability damage. Psionic characters can target nonpsionic opponents with attack modes, though nonpsionic creatures are naturally resistant to most such attacks.
\par 
\par Psionic Attack Modes\tab \tab Psionic Defense Modes
\par Ego Whip (Dex)\tab \tab Empty Mind
